WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.070
Hey, good morning, family. How are y'all

00:00:02.080 --> 00:00:04.309
doing today? Well, I have some things on

00:00:04.319 --> 00:00:06.630
my heart. You know, I told you all I was

00:00:06.640 --> 00:00:08.950
going to tell you about the economic

00:00:08.960 --> 00:00:10.790
crisis and everything that the Lord

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:13.270
showed me. I had the

00:00:13.270 --> 00:00:13.280
hour-long

00:00:13.280 --> 00:00:16.710
visitation vision, but the

00:00:16.720 --> 00:00:18.230
Lord said, 'Brandon, I need you to talk

00:00:18.240 --> 00:00:21.029
to tell them some more things first

00:00:21.039 --> 00:00:24.150
before you get to that.'I told

00:00:24.160 --> 00:00:26.550
you all about Israel and what I was

00:00:26.560 --> 00:00:30.310
praying for six months ago, and the Lord

00:00:30.320 --> 00:00:33.030
in my prayer time said, 'Brandon, this

00:00:33.040 --> 00:00:36.630
is a call to prayer again.

00:00:36.640 --> 00:00:38.709
Those things that you prophesied, the

00:00:38.719 --> 00:00:40.869
things that you warned them about, are

00:00:40.879 --> 00:00:43.670
trying to manifest right

00:00:43.670 --> 00:00:43.680
now.'The

00:00:43.680 --> 00:00:46.470
biological stuff that I saw—a secret attack in Paris coming out

00:00:46.480 --> 00:00:51.430
of a cave in Iran—was chemicals,

00:00:51.440 --> 00:00:53.430
and they were going to spray the people

00:00:53.440 --> 00:00:55.990
somehow. It was a secret

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:57.510
attack, just like it was in

00:00:57.520 --> 00:01:00.709
October. I want you to understand

00:01:00.719 --> 00:01:02.709
this; people are like, 'Well,

00:01:02.719 --> 00:01:05.189
nothing happened in Paris so far,

00:01:05.199 --> 00:01:08.070
you missed

00:01:08.070 --> 00:01:08.080
it.'Listen,

00:01:08.080 --> 00:01:12.710
my job is a Watchman. I come on here and

00:01:12.720 --> 00:01:15.510
tell you just like this:

00:01:15.520 --> 00:01:17.429
I'm looking out over the wall. I'm

00:01:17.439 --> 00:01:19.350
looking at the storm coming. There's a

00:01:19.360 --> 00:01:22.789
storm coming; let's pray.

00:01:22.799 --> 00:01:26.550
There are

00:01:26.550 --> 00:01:26.560
over 350,000

00:01:26.560 --> 00:01:30.469
people on this channel now. My job, when

00:01:30.479 --> 00:01:32.149
the Lord told me, He said, 'Brandon, I

00:01:32.159 --> 00:01:36.230
called you on YouTube to call an army of

00:01:36.240 --> 00:01:39.749
people of prayer—people who

00:01:39.749 --> 00:01:39.759
pray—and

00:01:39.759 --> 00:01:42.630
I want you to go on there and warn them

00:01:42.640 --> 00:01:45.030
of things that I'm going to show

00:01:45.030 --> 00:01:45.040
you.'The

00:01:45.040 --> 00:01:48.389
enemy has a plan to do certain

00:01:48.399 --> 00:01:51.350
things, and I want you to go on there

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:55.350
and you can change things with the body.

00:01:55.360 --> 00:01:58.950
My main job is to come on here and

00:01:58.960 --> 00:02:02.630
tell you, 'Hey, there are attacks in

00:02:02.640 --> 00:02:06.149
Paris planned by terrorists.'I see fires

00:02:06.159 --> 00:02:09.990
everywhere; I see an explosion,

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:12.229
and you need to pray over this. I saw a

00:02:12.229 --> 00:02:12.239
train—I

00:02:12.239 --> 00:02:13.830
told you everything the

00:02:13.840 --> 00:02:18.229
Lord showed me. So here we are; we see

00:02:18.239 --> 00:02:20.790
it. A man was busted coming

00:02:20.800 --> 00:02:22.550
out of Russia, and they

00:02:22.560 --> 00:02:25.830
found that he had

00:02:25.840 --> 00:02:29.190
plans and plots to create

00:02:29.190 --> 00:02:29.200
explosives,

00:02:29.200 --> 00:02:32.710
and he was found. What does

00:02:32.720 --> 00:02:35.350
that tell you? Not that I missed it

00:02:35.360 --> 00:02:37.830
because it didn't happen, but that God

00:02:37.840 --> 00:02:39.430
intervened.

00:02:39.440 --> 00:02:41.509
People go, 'Well, we didn't see

00:02:41.509 --> 00:02:41.519
anything.'Well,

00:02:41.519 --> 00:02:43.350
we don't want to!

00:02:43.360 --> 00:02:46.550
We want to see the hand of God

00:02:46.560 --> 00:02:50.150
protecting people. That's my job. I'm not on here to entertain you; this isn't entertainment. You click on YouTube and eat your popcorn and candy and sit there and go, 'Well, this is good. I want to eat another Snickers bar.'Come on, I'm

00:02:50.160 --> 00:02:53.430
here to tell you what's coming by the

00:02:53.440 --> 00:02:55.750
Spirit of the Lord and tell you we need

00:02:55.760 --> 00:02:58.150
to pray. There was fruit in that: a

00:02:58.160 --> 00:03:02.070
man was caught. Then the trains...

00:03:02.080 --> 00:03:03.750
another thing I'm seeing

00:03:03.750 --> 00:03:03.760
is

00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:05.110
trains. I told you all they're going to

00:03:05.120 --> 00:03:07.750
use trains; they set them on fire. I

00:03:07.760 --> 00:03:09.190
don't remember how many of them there were—I

00:03:09.190 --> 00:03:09.200
think there

00:03:09.200 --> 00:03:12.070
were about five of them.

00:03:12.080 --> 00:03:14.470
Obviously, I don't know if these

00:03:14.480 --> 00:03:16.550
men were caught, but the

00:03:16.560 --> 00:03:18.869
fires... I'm telling you, I see

00:03:18.879 --> 00:03:21.430
things on fire. I saw the area around the Eiffel

00:03:21.440 --> 00:03:24.390
Tower on

00:03:24.400 --> 00:03:27.670
fire. They didn't use any kind of

00:03:27.680 --> 00:03:29.910
pipe; they

00:03:29.910 --> 00:03:29.920
used

00:03:29.920 --> 00:03:33.430
fire.

00:03:33.440 --> 00:03:35.509
So I'm calling people to

00:03:35.519 --> 00:03:38.390
pray. 400,000 people

00:03:38.400 --> 00:03:42.789
watched that video, so we had a lot of

00:03:42.799 --> 00:03:44.949
people throughout the whole world

00:03:44.959 --> 00:03:48.869
praying for this not to happen. If

00:03:48.879 --> 00:03:51.750
one can put a thousand to

00:03:51.750 --> 00:03:51.760
flight—come

00:03:51.760 --> 00:03:54.070
on,

00:03:54.070 --> 00:03:54.080
folks—how

00:03:54.080 --> 00:03:57.030
much more can

00:03:57.040 --> 00:03:58.949
10,000 people? I'm just going to

00:03:58.949 --> 00:03:58.959
use

00:03:58.959 --> 00:04:01.429
the low number of people who take

00:04:01.439 --> 00:04:04.630
this seriously and say 10,000 people

00:04:04.640 --> 00:04:08.390
prayed. Like I said, there

00:04:08.390 --> 00:04:08.400
are 350,000

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:11.589
of you now, and I hope

00:04:11.599 --> 00:04:13.910
you take this

00:04:13.910 --> 00:04:13.920
seriously.

00:04:13.920 --> 00:04:15.589
The persecution of saying things is

00:04:15.599 --> 00:04:17.590
really ignorant.

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:19.430
But that's okay because you

00:04:19.440 --> 00:04:21.509
don't understand the spirit realm. This

00:04:21.519 --> 00:04:23.590
is what I have done my whole entire life

00:04:23.600 --> 00:04:26.070
since I've been sixteen years old.

00:04:26.080 --> 00:04:29.030
The Lord said to me, 'I want

00:04:29.040 --> 00:04:32.150
you to create an army of prayer

00:04:32.150 --> 00:04:32.160
people.'So

00:04:32.160 --> 00:04:34.550
I'm calling the troops, an army

00:04:34.550 --> 00:04:34.560
of prayer people,

00:04:34.560 --> 00:04:37.030
to tell you right now there is a

00:04:37.040 --> 00:04:39.909
plot to destroy a lot of lives in

00:04:39.919 --> 00:04:42.790
Israel. Then I come on here and tell you

00:04:42.800 --> 00:04:46.070
I see a major volcano going to explode

00:04:46.080 --> 00:04:49.189
in Italy, and it's going to

00:04:49.189 --> 00:04:49.199
cause

00:04:49.199 --> 00:04:51.909
a huge tsunami wave out of the water that is

00:04:51.919 --> 00:04:55.670
going to wipe out 300,000 people.

00:04:55.680 --> 00:04:58.150
People, I see the angels coming;

00:04:58.160 --> 00:04:59.990
they're warning the people.

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:02.070
We

00:05:02.080 --> 00:05:03.830
start seeing the volcanoes and

00:05:03.840 --> 00:05:05.590
earthquakes, and I told you all this was

00:05:05.600 --> 00:05:07.590
coming. I have an army of prayer

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:11.270
people interceding on behalf of

00:05:11.280 --> 00:05:14.310
Italy so that it won't happen.

00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:22.390
Just like Abraham interceded

00:05:22.390 --> 00:05:22.400
on

00:05:22.400 --> 00:05:25.270
behalf of Sodom and

00:05:25.270 --> 00:05:25.280
Gomorrah—he asked

00:05:25.280 --> 00:05:28.790
if there be fifty righteous.

00:05:28.800 --> 00:05:32.230
If God would do that for one

00:05:32.240 --> 00:05:34.629
person, a friend of God, how much more

00:05:34.639 --> 00:05:36.870
would He do it for 10,000? How much more

00:05:36.880 --> 00:05:39.350
would He do it for

00:05:39.350 --> 00:05:39.360
100,000

00:05:39.360 --> 00:05:41.670
if you would take seriously what

00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:43.990
I'm called to do: to come on here and

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:47.270
warn you of things to come.

00:05:47.280 --> 00:05:51.029
Not for fear, but as a call to

00:05:51.039 --> 00:05:53.909
prayer. I'm calling you to

00:05:53.919 --> 00:05:56.629
rise

00:05:56.639 --> 00:05:59.110
up and understand that we have

00:05:59.120 --> 00:06:02.150
authority as believers.

00:06:02.160 --> 00:06:04.469
We

00:06:04.479 --> 00:06:06.790
are seated with Him in the heavenlies,

00:06:06.800 --> 00:06:09.590
far above all principalities and powers.

00:06:09.600 --> 00:06:12.309
You have to understand who we are in

00:06:12.319 --> 00:06:15.029
Christ: that greater is He that is in

00:06:15.039 --> 00:06:17.749
you than he that is in the world. I'm

00:06:17.759 --> 00:06:20.070
not here to tell you

00:06:20.080 --> 00:06:21.830
doom and gloom; I'm trying to tell you

00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:24.790
the doom and gloom so we can stop it.

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:26.710
It's like

00:06:26.710 --> 00:06:26.720
the

00:06:26.720 --> 00:06:29.350
whack-a-mole;

00:06:29.360 --> 00:06:32.469
we're smacking the mole as the

00:06:32.479 --> 00:06:33.909
little things come up. The devil

00:06:33.919 --> 00:06:35.909
tries to raise his head, and

00:06:35.919 --> 00:06:38.150
we hit him.

00:06:39.840 --> 00:06:42.710
We're not trying to chase the

00:06:42.720 --> 00:06:45.270
devil around putting out his fires;

00:06:45.280 --> 00:06:47.270
we're trying to stop the fires before

00:06:47.280 --> 00:06:49.830
they start.

00:06:49.840 --> 00:06:51.590
Any

00:06:51.600 --> 00:06:54.710
calamity,

00:06:54.720 --> 00:06:56.950
destruction, or evil against the

00:06:56.960 --> 00:06:59.270
president, any politician, or

00:06:59.280 --> 00:07:01.909
anybody losing their life is of

00:07:01.919 --> 00:07:04.629
the devil. The Bible says that the thief

00:07:04.639 --> 00:07:06.950
comes to kill, steal, and destroy, but

00:07:06.960 --> 00:07:08.950
the Lord says, 'I have come that you

00:07:08.960 --> 00:07:10.950
might have life and life more

00:07:10.960 --> 00:07:12.469
abundantly.'God

00:07:12.479 --> 00:07:14.390
is not the boogeyman

00:07:14.400 --> 00:07:17.510
hurting people; the devil is.

00:07:19.759 --> 00:07:23.110
We as believers are called to raise a

00:07:23.120 --> 00:07:26.150
standard against him. The Lord said we

00:07:26.160 --> 00:07:27.990
could call on His angels.

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:29.749
Thank You,

00:07:29.759 --> 00:07:32.150
Lord, for Your angels in Psalms 91

00:07:32.150 --> 00:07:32.160
and

00:07:32.160 --> 00:07:35.510
Psalms 23. I believe with all my heart

00:07:35.520 --> 00:07:37.350
that we have authority over

00:07:37.360 --> 00:07:40.390
storms, pestilence,

00:07:40.390 --> 00:07:40.400
and

00:07:40.400 --> 00:07:42.870
plagues. I've warned you

00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:45.510
of

00:07:45.520 --> 00:07:48.950
attacks on our homeland

00:07:48.960 --> 00:07:50.790
with terrorists already here crossing

00:07:50.800 --> 00:07:53.510
the border.

00:07:53.520 --> 00:07:56.390
Now I'm trying to tell you about

00:07:56.400 --> 00:07:59.589
a financial crisis that

00:07:59.599 --> 00:08:05.189
is by design.

00:08:08.240 --> 00:08:10.710
My job is to come on here today

00:08:10.720 --> 00:08:12.629
and tell you about the attack against

00:08:12.639 --> 00:08:16.150
Israel. I stand with the Jews; I

00:08:16.160 --> 00:08:18.790
stand with Jerusalem; I pray

00:08:18.790 --> 00:08:18.800
for

00:08:18.800 --> 00:08:20.629
the peace of

00:08:20.639 --> 00:08:23.270
Jerusalem.

00:08:26.240 --> 00:08:27.909
Palestinians have lost their

00:08:27.909 --> 00:08:27.919
lives,

00:08:27.919 --> 00:08:30.230
and I pray for those families, but

00:08:30.240 --> 00:08:31.909
we're getting rid of

00:08:31.919 --> 00:08:34.630
the bad guys. I believe there are a lot of

00:08:34.640 --> 00:08:37.269
corrupt, evil people that wish harm on a

00:08:37.279 --> 00:08:39.269
lot of people—they're terrorists. But

00:08:39.279 --> 00:08:41.190
innocent lives are lost, and

00:08:41.200 --> 00:08:43.670
it's sad.

00:08:47.600 --> 00:08:50.230
I want peace. I want Jesus to

00:08:50.240 --> 00:08:52.949
rule and reign. But we

00:08:52.959 --> 00:08:55.110
have to pray for protection now because

00:08:55.120 --> 00:08:57.590
of Iran

00:08:57.600 --> 00:09:00.310
and what's about to happen. I'm

00:09:00.320 --> 00:09:01.750
calling you to my

00:09:01.750 --> 00:09:01.760
warning from

00:09:01.760 --> 00:09:04.230
six months ago: pray

00:09:04.230 --> 00:09:04.240
again.

00:09:04.240 --> 00:09:06.710
Six months ago, I warned

00:09:06.720 --> 00:09:09.190
you about a cave

00:09:09.190 --> 00:09:09.200
and

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:11.990
biological things. I

00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:14.070
warned you about them plotting an

00:09:14.080 --> 00:09:16.790
attack on our soil.

00:09:24.720 --> 00:09:27.350
I'm calling to shake you and blow

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:30.150
my trumpet in Zion. Sound the alarm on

00:09:30.160 --> 00:09:32.630
My holy mountain.

00:09:32.640 --> 00:09:37.350
Please listen to me.

00:09:46.640 --> 00:09:49.670
What the Lord showed me

00:09:49.670 --> 00:09:49.680
over

00:09:49.680 --> 00:09:53.509
the

00:09:53.519 --> 00:09:55.829
last couple of days

00:09:55.829 --> 00:09:55.839
regarding

00:09:55.839 --> 00:09:58.550
the

00:09:58.560 --> 00:10:01.430
crash of the stock market... He

00:10:01.440 --> 00:10:03.269
said, 'Brandon, this is just Braxton

00:10:03.279 --> 00:10:04.949
Hicks.'That's

00:10:04.959 --> 00:10:07.110
what Jesus

00:10:07.120 --> 00:10:08.790
said to me personally when I had my

00:10:08.790 --> 00:10:08.800
open-eye

00:10:08.800 --> 00:10:11.190
vision for an hour. He said, 'This

00:10:11.200 --> 00:10:14.389
is Braxton Hicks—what you're seeing in

00:10:14.389 --> 00:10:14.399
the economy.'There

00:10:14.399 --> 00:10:17.509
was a lot

00:10:17.519 --> 00:10:19.509
more, and I will give you that

00:10:19.519 --> 00:10:22.470
video shortly. The Lord said, 'I want

00:10:22.480 --> 00:10:25.030
you to focus on My people, Israel. Pray

00:10:25.040 --> 00:10:27.910
for them. Pray for this

00:10:34.720 --> 00:10:41.430
attack.'This

00:10:50.560 --> 00:10:53.350
economy stuff will not be stopped; it will

00:10:53.350 --> 00:10:53.360
come. But

00:10:53.360 --> 00:10:55.670
He said, 'I will

00:10:55.680 --> 00:10:59.190
always provide for

00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:01.030
My beloved.

00:11:01.040 --> 00:11:03.910
I will always take care of My beloved,

00:11:03.920 --> 00:11:06.790
Brandon, the great

00:11:06.790 --> 00:11:06.800
beloved—His

00:11:06.800 --> 00:11:10.710
child, us.'It gave me peace

00:11:10.720 --> 00:11:12.630
instantaneously because the things I saw

00:11:12.640 --> 00:11:15.990
in the spirit shook me.

00:11:16.000 --> 00:11:19.110
You

00:11:19.120 --> 00:11:20.870
could tell I cried a lot in that last

00:11:20.880 --> 00:11:22.870
video

00:11:22.880 --> 00:11:24.630
because the Spirit of the Lord was

00:11:24.640 --> 00:11:27.829
all over me.

00:11:27.839 --> 00:11:29.430
The experience that I had

00:11:29.440 --> 00:11:32.949
four or five nights ago

00:11:32.959 --> 00:11:35.990
changed my life forever.

00:11:38.150 --> 00:11:38.160
I

00:11:46.560 --> 00:11:48.150
can't even focus on it because if I

00:11:48.160 --> 00:11:49.829
look over and see His face

00:11:49.839 --> 00:11:53.910
again, Jesus melts me.

00:11:53.920 --> 00:12:09.030
Every

00:12:09.040 --> 00:12:12.790
time

00:12:12.800 --> 00:12:14.629
I start picturing His face and

00:12:14.629 --> 00:12:14.639
the way

00:12:14.639 --> 00:12:18.389
He looked calling His people... oh man.

00:12:23.440 --> 00:12:28.710
If I look at what I saw coming

00:12:28.720 --> 00:12:30.629
in the natural, it will cause

00:12:30.639 --> 00:12:33.670
you to fear. But when I saw

00:12:33.680 --> 00:12:36.949
Jesus's face and He said, 'I'll always

00:12:36.959 --> 00:12:39.590
take care of My beloved,'it

00:12:39.590 --> 00:12:39.600
wasn't

00:12:39.600 --> 00:12:42.790
about me; it

00:12:42.790 --> 00:12:42.800
was

00:12:42.800 --> 00:12:45.350
about a good God.

00:12:46.959 --> 00:12:50.470
When you

00:12:50.480 --> 00:12:53.750
abide in Him and His words abide in you,

00:12:53.760 --> 00:12:55.350
you shall ask what you will and

00:12:55.360 --> 00:13:00.150
it shall be done.

00:13:00.160 --> 00:13:02.069
Now I'm going

00:13:02.079 --> 00:13:04.230
to give you the rest of the sermon.

00:13:04.240 --> 00:13:06.870
Hey, good morning, family.

00:13:08.800 --> 00:13:10.710
I have some things on my

00:13:10.720 --> 00:13:13.110
heart

00:13:13.110 --> 00:13:13.120
regarding

00:13:13.120 --> 00:13:16.230
interceding

00:13:16.240 --> 00:13:20.069
for Israel and Iran. There is

00:13:20.069 --> 00:13:20.079
an escalation

00:13:20.079 --> 00:13:22.310
in the Middle East right now. One

00:13:22.310 --> 00:13:22.320
of the

00:13:22.320 --> 00:13:24.949
things

00:13:24.959 --> 00:13:27.750
that

00:13:27.760 --> 00:13:29.829
I felt a caution

00:13:29.839 --> 00:13:32.069
about was this thing

00:13:32.079 --> 00:13:35.670
going down in Cuba.

00:13:40.240 --> 00:13:42.150
I saw some secret meetings

00:13:42.150 --> 00:13:42.160
taking

00:13:42.160 --> 00:13:44.870
place, and the

